        "description": "Typical beam diameter for cleaning; 200 μm recommended for Silicon surface preparation, balancing resolution for fine features and coverage for larger areas. Smaller (50-100 μm) for detailed work; larger (300-500 μm) for broad contamination. Source: Equipment specs from Coherent ArmoClean systems; industry optimization in Surface and Coatings Technology (2020)."
